Construction bie2
	subcase of Morpheme
	form
		constraints	
			self.f.orth <-- "bie2"
	meaning: Negation
		evokes Warning as warning
		evokes Discourse_Segment as DS
		constraints
			self.m.process <--> warning.prohibited_action
			self.m.process.protagonist <--> warning.warned
			warning.warned <--> DS.addressee
			warning.warner <--> DS.speaker

